page.title: 19ONE BOY'S DAILY LIFE
page.content: I get up at 8:00a.m.get a wash and brush my teeth.I then go into my bedroom and get dressed.I go down stairs and have my breakfast.Then I get everything I need for school and get my money from my mum and set off for school. When I get to school I play cricket and when the bell goes I rush in and get my dinner mark and start working. I go out to play 3 times a day,early break time, dinner break time and last break time. When school has finished I go home and have my tea and go out to play until 9:00p.m.and have my supper and watch television and go to bed ready for the next morning.
